div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-ieecCq hEnArb pf-115_"><button type="button" class="sc-fotOHu cBHKWL pf-116_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="0d33fd63-9629-45eb-b78a-bc7bd7e4de54" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><span>HOW DO I RETURN OR EXCHANGE AN ITEM PURCHASED WITH AFFIRM?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0d33fd63-9629-45eb-b78a-bc7bd7e4de54" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-fFeiMQ fa-DBwG pf-118_"><div class="sc-dJjYzT drCpbA pf-119_ pf-r pf-c-ct" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:16px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-120_ pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-121_"><p class="sc-gGCDDS lbFTHT pf-122_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jQrDum heCnGO pf-124_"><p>Any Affirm purchases complies with our standard return policy. We accept returned merchandise in its original condition within 3 days of delivery. You will be responsible for the return shipping and 15% restocking fee.</p>

<p>If returned after 3 days, a merchandise credit will be issued at the discretion of Jade Trau.</p>

<p>All returns will go through Jade Trau’s quality control department before we can issue any return or merchandise credit. </p>

<p>After Jade Trau approves for a refund, the full amount will show up on your loan balance within 3 - 45 business days. You can check on your balance in your Affirm account.</p>

<p>While you are waiting for your refund, please make any monthly payments that are due.</p>

<p>If your refund is less than your total loan balance, it might not lower your next monthly payment. Instead you can expect fewer monthly payments, a smaller final payment, or both.</p>

<p>If your refund is more than your loan balance, you’ll get back the difference, minus any interest you’ve paid. We’ll credit your payment method within 3 - 10 business days. If you don’t have a payment method on file, you’ll get a check in the mail within 14 business days. </p>

<p>To initial or inquiry about a return please email us at: info@jadetrau.com. Our team will get back to you within 24 hours! </p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-125_ pf-hide"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-ieecCq hEnArb pf-126_"><button type="button" class="sc-fotOHu cBHKWL pf-127_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="6ca81169-3e3b-421b-921d-537e1cb2800b" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><span>CAN I CANCEL MY ORDER ONCE IT HAS BEEN PLACED?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="6ca81169-3e3b-421b-921d-537e1cb2800b" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-fFeiMQ fa-DBwG pf-129_"><div class="sc-dJjYzT drCpbA pf-130_ pf-r pf-c-ct" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:16px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-131_ pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-132_"><p class="sc-gGCDDS lbFTHT pf-133_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jQrDum heCnGO pf-135_"><p>Yes, cancellations can be made within 24 hours from the time the order was placed. Please contact info@jadetrau.com as soon as you can if you wish to cancel your order.</p>

<p>If your loan isn't finalized yet, we'll remove it from your Affirm account. It'll be like the loan never happened. </p>

<p>If your loan is already finalized, you'll get a full refund. You can expect the refund in about 21 days. </p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-136_ pf-hide"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-ieecCq hEnArb pf-137_"><button type="button" class="sc-fotOHu cBHKWL pf-138_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="7737c0d2-5b08-4f9f-ba11-b7ff55fca63d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><span>WHERE CAN I FIND MORE ABOUT AFFIRM?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7737c0d2-5b08-4f9f-ba11-b7ff55fca63d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-fFeiMQ fa-DBwG pf-140_"><div class="sc-dJjYzT drCpbA pf-141_ pf-r pf-c-ct" style="--s-xs:15px;--s-lg:16px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-142_ pf-hide"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-143_"><p class="sc-gGCDDS lbFTHT pf-144_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-jQrDum heCnGO pf-146_">Visit Affirm at: https://www.affirm.com/help/ for a list of FAQs and if you have questions about your Affirm account or order, please contact Affirm's customer support at: help@affirm.com! </span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c pf-hide" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:3;--c-lg:3"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jgrJph gHStpP pf-147_ pf-hide"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>window.__pagefly_setting__={"baseURL":"https://apps.pagefly.io","analyticsURL":"https://analytics.pagefly.io","isBackend":false,"cdnURL":"https://cdn.pagefly.io","pageflyVersion":"3.13.1","shopDomain":"jade-trau-dev.myshopify.com","elementData":{},"pageTitle":"Affirm","pageType":"page","pageId":"fe0a1327-afbb-4347-8b16